5.1 CSS Animation
  - <transition></transition>
  - v-enter
    - opacity 3s
  - v-enter-active
    - transition: opacity 3s
  - v-enter-to
  - v-leave
  - v-leave-active
  - v-leave-to

5.2 animate.css
  -https://animate.style/
  
5.3 multi style + animate
  - animate css -> @keyframes
  - transition
  - type/duration

5.4 JS animate/Velocity.js
  - js Animation hook
    - @before-enter
    - <transition @before-enter="functions"></transition>
    - var -> element(el)
      -> el.style.color='red';
    - @enter 
    - var -> el,done
      -> done() event. control when is done
      -> fire after enter
    - @after-enter
    - @before-leave,@leave,@after-leave
  - Velocity.js
    -http://www.velocityjs.org/

5.5 multi components Animation
  - v-if/v-else + KEY to avoid dom reuse
  - <transition mode="in-out"></transition>
  - pick a mode
  - for multi Components
    - v-if/v-else
    - dynamic components
      - <component :type=""></component>

5.6 LIST Animation
  - v-for="(item,index) of list" :key="index"
  - <transition-group></transition-group>

5.7 Animation reuse
  - use Components
    - prors: ['show']
    - template:
      <transition>
        <slot v-if="show"></slot>
      </transition>
  - use js Animation
    - put css into component
  
5.8 conclusion
https://cn.vuejs.org/v2/guide/transitions.html
